<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/style.css">
    <title>Main Screen</title>
    <% if (!isAuthenticated) { %>
    <button><a href="/login">로그인</a></button>
    <button><a href="/signup">회원가입</a></button>
    <% } else { %>
    <button><a href="/userscore">내 정보</a></button>
    <button><a href="/logout">로그아웃</a></button>
    <% } %>
    <h1><a href="/">Project Name</a></h1>

</head>

<body>
    <div align="center">
        <p>확인할 점수를 선택해주세요</p>
        <p>정보는 [내 정보]에서 수정 및 삭제 가능합니다</p>
        <br />
    </div>
    <table border="1" width="600px" cellspacing="0" align="center">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>월</th>
                <th>표준점수/백분위</th>
                <th>총합</th>
                <th></th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody align="center">
            <tr>
                <% for (let score of list) { %>
                <td><%= score.month %></td>
                <td><%= score.sp %></td>
                <td><%= score.sum %></td>
                <td>
                    <button><a href="/showrecom/<%= score.sum %>">추천 학과 보기</a></button>
                    <button><a href="/calcgrade/1">대학별 점수 보기</a></button>
                    <button><a href="/userscore">수정/삭제</a></button>
                </td>
                <% } %>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</body>

</html>